    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors were assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors met or exceeded required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved level 1 vs. required level 2) was accepted based on regulatory precedent and the clinical relevance of the single test configuration. All validation metrics satisfied pre-established acceptance criteria. The FEA framework is accepted as credible for the stated COU.",
